---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Our Homes — Inguz Care"
  description="Small, welcoming homes rooted in their communities."
>
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Our Homes</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg max-w-3xl">
      At Inguz Care, our homes are small, welcoming and rooted in their local communities.
      We design every space to feel calm, comfortable and truly homely—somewhere you can
      settle, belong and thrive.
    </p>

    <article class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border p-6 md:p-8">
      <header class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Radcliffe, Manchester</h2>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-[#eef5f4] text-[#3d5756] px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold">
          Opening soon
        </span>
      </header>

      <p class="mt-4">
        Our first home is opening in Radcliffe, Greater Manchester, in the coming months.
        Set in a friendly neighbourhood with easy access to local shops, green spaces and
        transport links, it’s a place where everyday life feels simple and supported.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Home highlights</h3>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Warm, comfortable bedrooms with room to personalise</li>
            <li>Bright shared spaces for meals, activities and relaxing</li>
            <li>A cosy lounge and homely kitchen at the heart of the house</li>
            <li>Outdoor space for fresh air and time in the garden</li>
            <li>Designed with safety, comfort and accessibility in mind</li>
            <li>Located close to local amenities and community activities</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">What you can expect</h3>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>A calm, respectful environment where people feel at home</li>
            <li>Person-centred support built around individual goals and preferences</li>
            <li>Consistent routines, clear communication and gentle structure</li>
            <li>Strong links with the local community to encourage connection and independence</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 rounded-xl bg-[#eef5f4] p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Be the first to know</h3>
        <p class="mt-2">
          We’re finalising the finishing touches now. If you’d like updates, to register your
          interest, or to arrange an early visit once we open, please get in touch.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="mt-4 inline-block px-5 py-3 rounded-lg bg-[#5f7c7b] text-white font-semibold hover:bg-[#3d5756]"
        >
          Register interest
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Growing thoughtfully</h3>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Radcliffe is just the beginning. We’re exploring additional homes across Greater
          Manchester and will share new locations as soon as they’re confirmed. If you’d like
          Inguz Care in your area, we’d love to hear from you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
